body_html:
@avmgithub Thanks for bringing to my attention that the tests aren't running in CircleCI. It looks like we only have coverage on macOS right now (https://ci.pytorch.org/jenkins/job/pytorch-builds/job/pytorch-macos-10.13-py3-test1/14585/console), where this error was not raised. I'll fix the CI of course.

As for you issue, I'll try to reproduce it.
